item.title: Moving forward the impostor syndrome
item.description: This article is a transcript of the eponymous talk I gave to Riviera Dev in Nice on May 16, 2019 and at VoxxedDays Luxembourg on June 22, 2019. The talk was filmed at Luxembourg, so you can watch it on Youtube (in french): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tvEVD4DyzpY&list=PL4PrrYCV-zckgY1yENIyftKU6AtF4kqkt Slides are also available online: http://bit.ly/syndrome-imposteur-kezako The principle of this transcript is simple: I first put the slide and then below the associated text / speech.
